Title: Fix required comment field on removing of downtimes
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1643706734
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

If downtimes were removed, a comment entry was required. This has been changed
to optional because for removements of downtimes, no comment is necessary.
